Output docs/demo/tui-smoke.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 1600
Set Height 900
Set Padding 24
Set FontFamily "JetBrainsMono Nerd Font Mono"
Set TypingSpeed 20ms
Hide
Type "cd /Users/saharbarak/workspace/forge"
Enter
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 200ms
Show
Type "forge start -m will-it-work -p TUITest -g "
Type@20ms `"Smoke test the new TUI layout"`
Type " -a skeptic,pragmatist,analyst --no-human -l english"
Enter
Sleep 3s
Type "0"
Enter
Sleep 60s
